This highly functional site is located within Seaford/Carrum Downs industrial precinct on Keppler Circuit. 

There is incredibly low vacancy within these two attractive precincts, mainly due to the immediate access onto such arterial roads as: Eastlink, Mornington Peninsula Fwy, Dandenong Valley Hwy and Nepean Hwy but also its proximity to Bayside residential catchments.

Property Features:
-	Dual level office incl. Welcoming reception area 
-	High clearance warehouse
-	5 container height roller doors 
-	Good power supply 
-	5 tonne crane
-	Huge hardstand area 
-	Excellent truck access 
-	Excellent natural light 

*approx

This property is located in the Heart of Carrum Downs industrial precinct, benefitting from immediate access onto the Mornington Peninsula FWY and the Frankston FWY.  

Property Features: 
-	Clear span warehouse of 918sqm
-	Well-presented dual level offices of 194sqm
-	Natural gas supply 
-	3 phase power 
-	Container height roller door 
-	Secure yard.

CBRE is excited to offer 14-16 Concord Crescent, Carrum Downs for sale via expressions of interest closing Wednesday 8th of September at 3pm AEST.

Located within the highly sought after Carrum Downs industrial market, the property offers excellent access to key arterials such as the Eastlink, Frankston Dandenong Road, Lathams Road and Peninsula Link, providing efficient access to all of metropolitan Melbourne and beyond.

Property features include:

-	1,009sqm* total building area
-	4,258sqm* total land area
-	Industrial 1 zone
-	Dual street cross overs
-	Two separate titles for future development
-	Fully fenced secure yard 
-	Abundance of on-site car parking
-	Large concrete hardstand 
-	3 phase power
